  "content": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "J2: Energy Efficiency"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "A building must have features that facilitate the efficient use of energy appropriate to:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "style": "bullet",
      "items": [
        "the function of the building; and",
        "the geographic location of the building; and",
        "the energy source."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The building envelope must be designed and constructed to reduce heat transfer and air leakage."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The building services must be designed and installed to facilitate the efficient use of energy."
    }
  ],
